title: adidas Skateboarding Silas ADV
description: Silas Baxter-Neal is known for his skateboarding, but did you know he’s really the brains behind adidas Skateboarding? Spend “a day in the life” with Silas, and see what exactly went into marketing his new shoe, the Silas ADV.
